Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这些也坏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能买新的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修好了还能用的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是非得新的才好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.12,0:00:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大学那边怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.47,0:00:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?还是那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.73,0:00:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有去好好上课吗?学分都拿到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为藤本君总是只顾着打工...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.84,0:00:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠又摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.84,0:00:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.44,0:00:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.71,0:00:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.81,0:01:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么走在平地上也会摔倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.70,0:01:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 谢谢

