Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[...好人.]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮忙 请让我也刷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:02:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...藤本先生...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点事想问你...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上嘴动手干活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然有动嘴的闲工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是问你想问什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.92,0:03:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.47,0:03:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...就是上次打进来的那个奇怪的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不能告诉清花老师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么总之就是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.53,0:03:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你非说不可的话 就不要再到这来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了她会难过的 所以不让你说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会难过...清花老师吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想帮忙还是想捣乱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又惹藤本先生生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生气了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为我总是妨碍他工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是去道个歉才好啊 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们陪你一起去道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(勿碰 刚刚刷过漆 不要碰)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是因为担心小鸠才生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的啊 小鸠 打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为希望你做个好孩子才生气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈告诉过我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我去道个歉 然后再拜托他让我帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 不在了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.49,0:05:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 一定是藤本君的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天他是不是要用的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 能帮忙给他送过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定正着急呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠去送!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了这是 这么起劲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:06:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他能认可我不只会捣乱也能帮上忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生在的大学走这边没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有听清楚走法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过大学是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这你都不知道就出来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 到现在也不会为你的无知而吃惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的大学就是学习各种很难的东西的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 有什么想做的事或者向往的工作的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人这么 人这么多...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是大学嘛 这点人不算多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有几个艾草保育院那么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有空比较啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧找那小子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!五百祗先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FIGHT FIGHT FIGHT...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起~~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...那个...啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷个屁的路啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...找不到啊 藤本先生...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是在大学里乱转悠而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 会加油的!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.94,0:07:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发什么呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 得把这个送过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别再犯傻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.16,0:08:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱的玩偶啊 给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...你是清和的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是...还说不上是朋友...那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像朋友一样?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是堂元 崇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.65,0:08:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我叫花户小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来送藤本先生忘记的东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚确实在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才也惹他生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:08:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他又生气了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生动不动就发脾气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不过不过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是因为我总是什么都做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我觉得他发脾气太过火了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...可是...也一直也都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生也没有什么错...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊 你是艾草保育园的?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.13,0:09:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那里帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 我们一起去找清和吧 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找藤本先生吗 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是不方便?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时间的话 大概是法哲学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我想他今天一整天都在大学里哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在打工也减少了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快要考试了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生一直都很忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想要钱的话明明有那么多种选择
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可却以打工优先
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.78,0:10:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这才是清和的一贯作风呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想请你帮个忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给早川教授的报告不知道该从何下手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然要我们下个礼拜交出来你说过不过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 堂元君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说在前面 我只是帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你们要自己写哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们当然明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:10:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本?没看见他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.11,0:11:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会在图书馆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 如果看到他 能不能转告他我正在找他?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.59,0:11:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙平常就不合群 感觉很可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很害怕藤本先生吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢 不够亲切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都板着副面孔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元先生也害怕他吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你说你惹藤本先生生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本也有生我的气的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一向是个不需要别人帮助的类型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我却对他说了些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在给他的将来提建议一样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明从以前就知道的很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是忍不住多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 因为不能放着不管嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等着呢 快点来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天藤本君和小鸠都不在 很无聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没...没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再稍等一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师 有客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是千帆和千世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千岁 你怎么来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们和妈妈三人做了杏仁小圆饼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.65,0:12:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以拿来给大家吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松松脆脆的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花 清和君和小鸠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们俩今天都去大学了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠她也?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本?他刚才已经出去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 谢谢了 我去别处找好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 堂元
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和富田教授关系很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今年如果学分拿不到就不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帮我求求情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己已经去说过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没...因为很难为情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先请面子大的堂元君帮我打个招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?感恩戴德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后你自己也要去跟教授...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都找堂元先生帮忙呢 五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去个别的地方行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:14:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说 他的出勤率实在是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.29,0:14:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也在深刻地反省了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托您了 富田教授
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.75,0:14:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 既然你都说到这个份上了...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.55,0:14:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元先生你真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害?什么厉害?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都来请你帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也帮助了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想成为对大家有用的人 却总也做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真厉害 堂元先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢...可以这样说吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪子布
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 输了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 千帆当鬼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 大家 快藏起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊 所以就去大学...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像干劲十足的样子呢 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像小鸠的风格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 清花 你看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由香里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千世?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪位?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿?抓住由香里了~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是千帆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位说如果要融资的话可以找他谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是我认识的会计师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 这位是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 千岁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花 你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是因为觉得你可怜才帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:16:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里是我和千帆千世呆过的艾草保育园
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想要守护她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不可以道歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们只是翘课了而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想去帮这种人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 不愿帮忙就说不愿意不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我不愿意 我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 早知道就不找那种家伙帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么在这
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生你好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么非得故意那样说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种故意惹人生气的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不那样说的话 她们还会缠个没完
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.06,0:16:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家也许有人家的苦衷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的事情要自己解决
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘记的东西 我可是拿过来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说了那种话...我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本来帮我找藤本先生的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然忘了道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠和清和什么时候认识的?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...今年春天认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:17:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有点羡慕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.71,0:18:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠和清和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和藤本先生吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然在很早就认识他了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也不能像小鸠你一样和他说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生果然觉得不开心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是做了失礼的事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠你说的是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是虽然是对的我却说不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 做不到的事再怎么说也没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得堂元先生有着很多优点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如很温柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点也不温柔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你会听大家的请求去帮助大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.78,0:18:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很温柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是啊 因为我不擅长拒绝别人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的是为了对方好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是像清和一样拒绝了才对的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们只是翘课了而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想去帮这种人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.49,0:19:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和他不怕被其他人讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个坚强的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围的人会疏远他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为这份坚强令人望而却步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人羡慕啊 这份坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.21,0:19:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份坚强...令人羡慕?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不是很了解藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我觉得被人害怕的话会很孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人讨厌的话会很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天遇见的人在受到堂元先生的帮助时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那个是....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让人讨厌这种想法是不对的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望被人喜欢的想法是错的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去帮助人就是错的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想为觉得困窘的人做些什么是错的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.66,0:20:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也说不大清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元先生 是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.84,0:20:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.61,0:20:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个不可思议的女孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 难道我说了什么奇怪的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.03,0:20:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因为什么也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以常常被五百祗先生骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 五百祗先生虽然是个布偶但是会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是虽然可以说话却叫我不要和他说话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个布偶就是五百祗先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 刚刚的...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:20:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是 非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.65,0:21:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么金平糖又...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你认可了那个小白脸的温柔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小白脸?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元先生吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的还有谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是 只是认可这点小事金平糖就会...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有对其他人不觉得 但是本人很在意的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 也就是说小白脸也有小白脸的烦恼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来土鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于白天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.14,0:21:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.33,0:21:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么把我的事全告诉那小子了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正如五百祗先生你所说的没有和你说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.47,0:21:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我身为玩偶却会说话告诉他就是死罪!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.24,0:21:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三十分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧~~怎么能这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.59,0:22:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你帮了我忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.55,0:22:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本君真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.26,0:22:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.98,0:22:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不老实啊 那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.20,0:22:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那已经算是努力对你道谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.44,0:22:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道谢?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和老师已经不生气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用怕哦 清和老师人很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.90,0:22:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.95,0:22:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满里奈家里的钥匙不见的时候也帮我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.89,0:22:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还做了竹灯给我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.93,0:22:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 他还给我知了蜕的皮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对...还有知了蜕的皮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.36,0:22:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:22:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是坏孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.54,0:22:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个不可思议的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.70,0:22:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生

Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.23,0:24:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}[...小猫的摇篮曲.]


Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.58,0:23:09.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}人はみな飛んでみたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.39,0:23:16.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}重力に騙されてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.84,0:23:24.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}誰もほんとは飛べるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:33.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あの子があんなに悲しそうなのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.17,0:23:44.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}自分の影をどこかに忘れてきちゃったからかも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.45,0:23:46.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.08,0:23:51.11,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君に言えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.28,0:23:55.11,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君が笑えば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.31,0:24:02.50,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いったりきたり　嬉しくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.87,0:24:07.25,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}君が幸せになる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.48,0:24:11.67,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}心配なんていらないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.84,0:24:16.06,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.54,0:24:28.84,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しくても涙が出るなんて不思議だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.58,0:23:09.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明明人们都是那么想飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.39,0:23:16.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只不过被重力所欺骗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.84,0:23:24.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}其实谁都可以在天上翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:33.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}那个孩子为什么如此悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.17,0:23:44.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}也许是把自己的影子忘在了哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.45,0:23:46.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}是那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.08,0:23:51.11,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能对你说 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.28,0:23:55.11,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能看见你的笑容 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.31,0:24:02.50,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}来来往往中 变得愉悦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.87,0:24:07.25,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你一定能变得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.48,0:24:11.67,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}不需要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.84,0:24:16.06,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}因为我们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.54,0:24:28.84,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}喜极而泣总是那么不可思议
